title: Shoes and Stockings: A Collection of Short Stories
creator: Louisa May Alcott
description: Librivox recording of Shoes and Stockings: A Collection of Short Stories by Louisa May Alcott read by Carolyn Frances. Here are tales of love and war, modesty and frivolity, laughter and tears. Louisa May Alcott wrote many, many short stories. This collection shares but 7 of them. Summary by Carolyn Frances. M4B format available For more free audiobooks or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org
subject: librivox;  audiobook;  literature; romance; humor;
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: A nice collection of Louisa May Alcott stories, they will make you laugh and cry!  My favorites are Kitty's Class Day and Aunt Kipp.  Also, Carolyn does an awesome job reading A Country Christmas, especially in part 2.
